    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts exactly as it should, making it a reliable choice for any commute. While the exterior is clean, you may find some minor rock chips on the hood and light scratches consistent with careful use. The interior is in great shape with no tears in the upholstery, and all electronic features are fully functional. This is a solid, turn-key car that offers a great balance of quality and value.",
