      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true automotive masterpiece in showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, retaining its original deep-luster factory paint and a flawless exterior free of stone chips or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and shows zero signs of bolster wear, while the carpets are protected by original, heavy-duty mats. Every electronic component, from the navigation system to the heated seats, functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule with all records included. It drives with the tightness and smoothness of a brand-new vehicle, offering an unparalleled experience for the discerning collector who demands perfection. Complete with all original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover.",
      "price": 48500.0,
